# RTL & Urdu

Root: `lang="ur" dir="rtl"` on `<html>` — do not override without reason.

## Layout
- Logical spacing: `ms-*` / `me-*` / `ps-*` / `pe-*` / `start-*` / `end-*` — **not** `ml-*` / `mr-*`
- Directional icons: `rtl:rotate-180` on arrows/chevrons in nav
- Body text: `leading-[1.8]` minimum (Nastaliq glyphs)
- Touch targets: `TW_TOUCH` (`min-h-11`) from `lib/tailwind.ts`

## Copy
**All user-visible text in Urdu.** Run `npm run check:urdu`. False positive: `// urdu-ok`

Full allow/deny table: `CLAUDE.md` § Urdu-First Frontend Rule.

## Motion
`prefers-reduced-motion` handled in `Reveal.tsx` and `globals.css`.

Skill: `rtl-check` after nav/layout changes.
